OL,3,CPSNI staff strike action postponed
OL,4,Cafter 'danger money' agreement
OL,6,FPlanned strike action by police
OL,7,Fcivilian staff later this week has
OL,8,Fbeen postponed following an interim
OL,9,Fagreement over danger money payments.
OL,11,FThe industrial action was scheduled to
OL,12,Ftake place across July 11-13, one of
OL,13,Fthe busiest periods for policing in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland when annual Orange
OL,15,FOrder and Royal Black Preceptory
OL,16,Fparades take place as well as loyalist
OL,17,Fbonfires.
