OL,3,CPSNI staff strike action postponed
OL,4,Cafter 'danger money' agreement
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the trade union Nipsa said
OL,7,Fan interim agreement had been reached
OL,8,Fwith the PSNI over the revised
OL,9,Fenvironmental allowance (REA).
OL,11,FIn a statement, Nipsa said it came
OL,12,Fafter intense negotiations for an
OL,13,Fincrease and improved terms of the REA
OL,14,Ffor police staff.
OL,16,FHowever they warned the interim
OL,17,Fagreement has not fully resolved the
OL,18,Fdispute, adding that action short of
OL,19,Fstrike action will continue and
OL,20,Ffurther strike action will be
OL,21,F"considered if necessary".
