OL,3,CPSNI staff strike action postponed
OL,4,Cafter 'danger money' agreement
OL,6,FIn a statement on Tuesday, Nipsa said:
OL,7,F"A series of meetings have taken place
OL,8,Fover the last few weeks with the Chief
OL,9,FConstable, the Justice Minister for
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and the Policing
OL,11,FBoard and these have led to the
OL,12,Fdecision to postpone the planned
OL,13,Fstrike action.
OL,15,F"It has been agreed that some of the
OL,16,Fterms on the business case, and a lump
OL,17,Fsum payment of REA, will be put in
OL,18,Fplace as soon as possible.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
