OL,6,F"This interim measure will allow
OL,7,Fadditional time to achieve full
OL,8,Fimplementation of the business case
OL,9,Fand continue negotiations and as a
OL,10,Fresult, the planned action has been
OL,11,Fcalled off and the PSNI staff will
OL,12,Fremain operational this week.
OL,14,F"This does not fully resolve the
OL,15,Findustrial dispute and the action
OL,16,Fshort of strike action will continue
OL,17,Fand further strike action will be
OL,18,Fconsidered if necessary.
