OL,6,F"However, Nipsa has been given
OL,7,Fassurances that REA will be
OL,8,Fprioritised for full resolution in the
OL,9,Fcoming months and Nipsa remain
OL,10,Fcommitted to resolving this dispute
OL,11,Fthrough negotiation."
OL,13,FStormont Justice Minister Naomi Long
OL,14,Fwelcomed the move.
OL,16,F"The announcement by Nipsa to suspend
OL,17,Fstrike action is welcome and shows a
OL,18,Freal and shared determination by all
OL,19,Fparties to resolve this long-standing
OL,20,Fissue to a successful conclusion," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
