OL,6,F"I remain conscious of the need to
OL,7,Fundertake due diligence for public
OL,8,Ffunds, however the discussions with
OL,9,FNipsa yesterday, and the proposal made
OL,10,Flast week, should offer reassurance to
OL,11,Fmembers.
OL,13,F"I do not underestimate the crucial
